                       <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2000Mazmur">Mazmura Dāwit</title>
                       <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ'ǝz</textLang>
                       <note>Introduction:
                      <foreign xml:lang="gez">እስመ መዝሙረ ዳዊት ትመስል ገነተ
                      ወታስተጋብዕ ጽጌያተ ትመልዕ ፍሬያተ
                      ታመጽእ በረከተ ትሰድድ አጋንንተ
                      ወታቀርብ መላእክተ</foreign>
                      The Psalms of David are like a garden
                      It gathers flowers and is filled with fruit
                      It brings blessing and drives out demons
                      And it brings near the angels
                      </note>
                     </msItem>

